net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component

Enum TextElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<TextElement>
      • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.TextElement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<TextElement>, net.proteusframework.core.html.Element

    public enum TextElement
extends Enum<TextElement>
implements net.proteusframework.core.html.Element
    Defines HTML elements that are intended to contain text. Note that this is a subset of HTML elements. For example, "table" does not belong here because it is not used to denote text content.
    Author:
    Pat Double (double@i2rd.com)
